{"id":244900,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/08/维权网-北京市民李学会等人前往北戴河遭扣押/","date":"2012-08-03T23:46:12Z","modified":"2012-08-03T23:46:12Z","title":"维权网 | 北京市民李学会等人前往北戴河遭扣押","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-FFO5T_YEDG0/UBxT7FcYRvI/AAAAAAAAKvI/ZY47aASaHe8/s1600/20120802_1323_1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-FFO5T_YEDG0/UBxT7FcYRvI/AAAAAAAAKvI/ZY47aASaHe8/s1600/20120802_1323_1.jpg\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>李学会（右）与郭建立</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员姚立法报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>日</span><span>，北京市民李学会、叶洪霞和郭建立三人结伴驾车前往北戴河旅游。近</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>时，他们在秦皇岛北戴河检查站被警方扣押，其身份证也被搜走。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>昨晚</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>点</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>分，郭建立被丰台区警方等部门的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>人抬上车带走。叶洪霞于昨夜</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>时被海淀区信访局的人员“接”</span><span> </span><span>走。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>日</span><span>凌晨两点，李学会被石景山区八角派出所警察“接回”</span><span></span><span>。警方的说法是――北戴河是敏感地区，像李学会这样的人不能去。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>当晚近</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>点钟，李学会获得自由。</span><span>李学会表示，他们将到公安部去控告基层警方非法拦截、扣押公民、限制其人身自由的行为。　</span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-9186650481582650441?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/po